data.title: General FAQs
data.text:
Proof of the Pudding is the exclusive caterer at The Carter Center. All food and beverage, including alcohol, must be provided by Proof of the Pudding. For information regarding menus and pricing, please contact our account executive listed under Exclusive Vendors located on the lower right-hand corner of this page.

Door signs will be posted on each set of doors directing guests to the correct entrance.

Ivan Allen III Pavilion Main Entrance - Events in the Cecil B. Day Chapel or Ivan Allen III Pavilion Main Foyer.

Executive Offices Entrance - Events in the Cyprus Room, Rotunda/Upper Commons, Lower Commons, Zaban Room or Executive Dining Room.

Museum Main Entrance - Events in the Library Lobby and Copenhill Cafe.
